languages.text: "Нас было больше: пятеро умерли от истощения, трое — в результате обвала десятинного имущества, двоих съели амбуллы, а еще десять... нацать... Я не знаю! Пополнения от Администратума очень редки — этот мир слишком секретный!"

"There used to be more of us. Five died of exhaustion. Three were killed in collapses of tithe assets. Two were eaten by ambulls. Another ten... no, elev— I don't know! Administratum replenishments are too rare! This world is too highly classified!"

languages.text: “这里原本还有其他职员，但五个人被累死了，三个人被什一税活埋了，两个人被蚁牛吃了，还有另外十个人……不对，十一个——我也说不好！内政部的人员补充根本不够！这个世界的保密级别太高了！”
languages.original_text: "There used to be more of us. Five died of exhaustion. Three were killed in collapses of tithe assets. Two were eaten by ambulls. Another ten... no, elev— I don't know! Administratum replenishments are too rare! This world is too highly classified!"

languages.text: 「かつてはもっとたくさんいました。疲労により5人死にました。3人が租税の破損で殺されました。2人はアンブルに食べられました。他の10人、いや11人は―知りません！行政局の補充は非常にまれなのです！この惑星は極秘にされすぎています！」
languages.original_text: "There used to be more of us. Five died of exhaustion. Three were killed in collapses of tithe assets. Two were eaten by ambulls. Another ten... no, elev— I don't know! Administratum replenishments are too rare! This world is too highly classified!"

languages.text: « Nous étions plus nombreux avant, mais cinq de mes collègues sont morts d'épuisement. Trois autres ont trouvé la mort sous des avalanches de tributs de la dîme. Deux ont été dévorés par des ambulls. Et les dix restants... non, onze... rah, je ne sais plus ! Les renforts envoyés par l'Administratum sont trop rares ! Et pour cause, l'existence de ce monde est hautement confidentielle ! »
languages.original_text: "There used to be more of us. Five died of exhaustion. Three were killed in collapses of tithe assets. Two were eaten by ambulls. Another ten... no, elev— I don't know! Administratum replenishments are too rare! This world is too highly classified!"

languages.text: "Eskiden daha fazlaydık. Beşi yorgunluktan öldü. Üçü aşar varlıklarının çökmesiyle öldü. İkisini ambullar yedi. Diğer on... Yok, on bir... Of, bilmiyorum! Administratum takviyeleri çok nadirdir! Bu dünya da aşırı yüksek derecede gizli!"
languages.original_text: "There used to be more of us. Five died of exhaustion. Three were killed in collapses of tithe assets. Two were eaten by ambulls. Another ten... no, elev— I don't know! Administratum replenishments are too rare! This world is too highly classified!"

languages.text: "Früher gab es mehr von uns. Fünf starben an Erschöpfung. Drei wurden von herabfallenden Abgaben erschlagen. Zwei wurden von Ambullen gefressen. Weitere zehn ... nein elf... keine Ahnung! Das Administratum schickt nur selten frische Kräfte! Die Geheimhaltungsstufe dieser Welt ist einfach zu hoch!"
